e-height: 2; font-size: 11pt; font-family: 等线;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">2</span><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">、商家存在恶意竞争、影响消费者权益、影响京东平台声誉等违反市场公平竞争原则、诚实信用原则、公序良俗的行为；</span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 8pt; line-height: 2; font-size: 11pt; font-family: 等线;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">3</span><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">、违反《<a style=\"color: #467886; text-decoration: underline;\" href=\"https://rule.jd.com/rule/ruleDetail.action?ruleId=2614\">京东开放平台招商资质标准细则》</a>的行为；</span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 8pt; line-height: 2; font-size: 11pt; font-family: 等线;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">4</span><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">、违反《<a style=\"color: #467886; text-decoration: underline;\" href=\"https://rule.jd.com/rule/ruleDetail.action?ruleId=2754\">京东开放平台商家违规管理总则》</a>的行为；</span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 8pt; line-height: 2; font-size: 11pt; font-family: 等线;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">5</span><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">、违反其他京东平台规则的行为。</span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 8pt; line-height: 2; font-size: 11pt; font-family: 等线;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">&nbsp;</span></p>",
